  "text": "One can see geometrically that the relative Gromov-Witten invariantH g,µ is equal to the Hurwitz number H g,µ . This together with (23) gives a proof of the ELSV formula presented in [CITATION_1] Section 7] in the spirit of [CITATION_2] . Note thatH g,µ = H g,µ is not used in the proof described above.",
